column2: SELECT ALL ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY s.ra ASC) as RowNumber, s.ra, s.dec, s.z, sigma_balmer, sigma_forbidden, oii_#_reqw, neiii_#_reqw, oiii_#_reqw, hei_#_reqw, oi_#_reqw, h_alpha_reqw, nii_#_reqw, sii_#_reqw, h_delta_eqw, h_gamma_eqw, h_beta_eqw, h_alpha_eqw FROM GalSpecLine AS g JOIN SpecObj AS s ON s.specobjid = g.specobjid WHERE s.class = &&& AND s.zwarning = # AND s.ra BETWEEN # and #
